    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1944-12-07T13:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-12-07T13:00:00-05:00" n="291"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d291">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">871.01/12–744: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The American Representative in Rumania</hi> (<persName
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Berry</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bucharest</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-12-07T20:00:00+02:00"
                            >December 7, 1944—8 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received December 8—2:50 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>50. Steps involved in forming the new government will be reported by
                        despatch.<note n="86" xml:id="d291fn1">No. 24, December 8, not
                        printed.</note> However, it is considered locally that the Radescu Cabinet,
                    together with the agreed program, constitute a victory, at least temporarily,
                    over the National Democratic Front composed of the Leftist parties. Responsible
                    sources claim that Soviet pressure caused the Left suddenly to enter Radescu
                    Government after first refusing to participate. On this point it is of interest
                    that one report states that at a large official reception Tuesday evening at the
                    Soviet Legation Deputy Commissar Vishinsky, in the course of an agreeable
                    conversation with General Radescu, complimented him on virtually solving the
                    political crisis by forming a government of all political parties.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Berry</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
